<p id="biaoti">Sanrio Amusement Park, Tokyo, Japan</p>
<div class="content-row">
    <img src="/Content/park1.PNG" class="tab1photo" style="margin:30px" />
    <p id="content-para">Tokyo Sanrio Rainbow Land is an indoor theme park operated by Sanrio Company, featuring characters such as Hello Kitty, My Melody, Cool Penguin, Little Twin Stars and Pudding Dog. It is located in Tama City, Tokyo, Japan, and is one of the most popular theme parks in Japan. In Rainbow Land, there are many cartoon stars from the dream kingdom. The grand sound, light and work "Warm Parade Believe" will bring together these big stars! The main program is musicals and performances. "Hello Kitty's Nutcracker" features Kitty and her family on stage. The park is best known for its carnival-style parade, followed by 7 entertainment facilities,3 restaurants, 1 cafe and 4 gift shops. Here, you will have the most special experience, feel the real warmth and touching, let you linger.</p>
</div>
