<p id="biaoti">HelloKitty Paradise in Hangzhou</p>
<div class="content-row">
    <img src="/Content/park2.jpg" class="tab1photo" style="margin:30px" />
    <p id="content-para">Hello Kitty and her friends call this beautiful and innocent home Hangzhou Hello Kitty Paradise and have built a square in the middle of it. Every day, the small partners will gather in this square, and you will talk about what kind of surprise you will give to the people here tomorrow. Everyone who comes here can gain friendship here. All kinds of show and float parade, Asia's first Ferris wheel slide, China's most complete HelloKitty cutie. This is Hello Kitty's first overseas home, the park covers an area of 400 acres, the park 11 sets of large-scale amusement facilities, will be happy port, sound village, spirit Forest, power connection, Hello Kitty home five areas. Kitty and her friends treat everyone who comes from afar with the most sincere warmth and friendship.</p>
</div>
